data.description: Welcome to this 4 bedroom Park Place home! Featuring a huge backyard which is perfect for those outdoor gatherings along with a basement that is primed to finish for your entertainment cave. The owners suite comes with a sizable room and ''His & Hers'' closets. Home also features 1-floor laundry, a 2-car garage and a formal dining room. Schedule your showing today to view your next home! Conveniently close to Route 256, Freeways, Shopping and Entertainment.** Agents please read A2A**
